Package org.yawlfoundation.yawl.engine.interfce.interfaceB

Client and server -side interfaces for instance and work item execution.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InterfaceBClient
    Defines the 'B' interface into the YAWL Engine corresponding to WfMC interfaces 2+3 - Workflow client applications and invoked applications.
    InterfaceBClientObserver
    Defines the 'B' interface into the YAWL Engine corresponding to WfMC interfaces 2+3 - Workflow client applications and invoke applications.
    InterfaceBInterop
    Defines the 'B' interface into the YAWL Engine corresponding to WfMC interfaces 4 - Workflow engine interoperability.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IBControllerCache  
    InterfaceB_EngineBasedClient
    This interface announces specific Engine events to listening custom services
    InterfaceB_EngineBasedServer
    Receives & responds to POST messages from custom services
    InterfaceB_EnvironmentBasedClient
    An API for custom services to call Engine functionalities regarding workitem management, process progression and case state.
    InterfaceB_EnvironmentBasedServer
    Receives event announcements from the engine and passes each of them to the custom service's appropriate handling method
    InterfaceB_HttpsEngineBasedClient  
    InterfaceBWebsideController
    An abstract class designed to be implemented by YAWL custom services.
